The paper deals with shape retrieval, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The method proposed in the paper involves both global and local features, which are commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) applications. The paper also mentions the use of machine learning techniques to predict the relevance of shapes, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
